g src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n麥皮要用奶，唔敢飲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"邊個話要用奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7fbd386c589d9524f1b1bad1c854491e68ad4f","tid":724913,"uid":53089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"胃鏡照左未？"},{"pid":"36003fd830aa59d5f51ebfce762092a4faef6329","tid":724913,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"成年前都係咁<br />\n無咁嚴重地痛但仲有胃脹<br />\n成日食少少想嘔<br />\n最後係神經緊張搞到胃功能失調<br />\n又係驗血照哂胃鏡都冇咩大問題<br />\n靜係十二指腸有2mm erosion <br />\n最後食tca 好左好多<br />\n不過一忙/大壓力又會返發<br />\n樓主試過咩藥?"},{"pid":"fa20cf98811db52968196ffcc7fb69c07f632ae0","tid":724913,"uid":192891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"我女朋友都係咁 有排好嚴重 感覺上係生活習慣同壓力所至"},{"pid":"b1402b1d351f9feaa23391307698d398691febef","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胃鏡照左未？</blockquote><br />\n照咗，輕微胃炎"},{"pid":"56488828fccfc879701c98eb89d29df50a1d094c","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點痛法？我都成日痛</blockquote><br />\n痛到企唔直，訓醒條腰硬哂<br />\n一食野就痛 唔食又好肚餓</blockquote>有冇試過食麥皮一段時間睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n麥皮要用奶，唔敢飲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>邊個話要用奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日買黎試下"},{"pid":"0f4b0e70e94a618e2bf8bf262a23cf6b1ecca6e6","tid":724913,"uid":14794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"照胃鏡痛唔痛，我之前都有 痛到企唔直個身，又會半夜痛醒，好辛苦。我係唔食野空肚就胃痛，食野就無事。但好彩睇完醫生就無事，要介辣同奶茶，食野要嘴饞耐啲，之前食野好快，五分鐘食完個飯。"},{"pid":"992092bb7fef64b7453e07f1dadcd0c023225fcb","tid":724913,"uid":20386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:07:54.000Z","msg":"食白粥/小米粥 好過食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\n(純粹個人經驗)"},{"pid":"1c678ba87d740c8b67d4a4300d34d967e9e3b559","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成年前都係咁<br />\n無咁嚴重地痛但仲有胃脹<br />\n成日食少少想嘔<br />\n最後係神經緊張搞到胃功能失調<br />\n又係驗血照哂胃鏡都冇咩大問題<br />\n靜係十二指腸有2mm erosion <br />\n最後食tca 好左好多<br />\n不過一忙/大壓力又會返發<br />\n樓主試過咩藥?</blockquote><br />\nOmeprazole, escomeprazole, pantoprazole, 加衛斯康，famotidine等等N種胃藥<br />\n專科醫生開過類固醇止痛藥<br />\n仲有幫助消化，腸痛肚痛等等<br />\n普通科醫生試過痛博士 但治標不治本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2084a5223bf85efc84b41f313b3604decfa6606a","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我女朋友都係咁 有排好嚴重 感覺上係生活習慣同壓力所至</blockquote><br />\n日日痛 開心又痛 唔開心又痛<br />\n最慘試過一個鐘狂嘔50次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ed33fe977c85e0057d0ea8cecd6499249adea0","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照胃鏡痛唔痛，我之前都有 痛到企唔直個身，又會半夜痛醒，好辛苦。我係唔食野空肚就胃痛，食野就無事。但好彩睇完醫生就無事，要介辣同奶茶，食野要嘴饞耐啲，之前食野好快，五分鐘食完個飯。</blockquote><br />\n私家照唔痛，打啲鎮靜劑就訓咗<br />\n我同你相反，一食就痛，搞到唔敢食<br />\n輕咗幾磅，本身已經過輕<br />\n已戒口，食量少到一個飯分三餐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c096db30efbc19746b64ddd25b4e35100a8440ce","tid":724913,"uid":85232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"我都成日肚痛，腸鏡胃鏡做埋咩事都冇，醫生話我腸易激，好影響生活，咩都做唔到。係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef735dbbe2686a2bc82f8dc50e662b52b4d3b80","tid":724913,"uid":100772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"我以前都係  後來知道食某類野會敏感 之後唔食好番D"},{"pid":"2c4203b6fb9a1c2de9a05f7f7a0d36edc1b29dec","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都成日肚痛，腸鏡胃鏡做埋咩事都冇，醫生話我腸易激，好影響生活，咩都做唔到。係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我都係，大腸燥激<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c84d77938fe33ad80d83d2fc2ea6ece9bfd990","tid":724913,"uid":88957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前都係  後來知道食某類野會敏感 之後唔食好番D</blockquote><br />\n食咩敏感？"}]}